7. Cost-benefit ratio: In financial planning, especially for office equipment, the cost-benefit ratio is crucial. The inclusion of high-end gaming components is unlikely to offer a favorable cost-benefit ratio for an office setup, as they do not enhance productivity in an office context.

8. Misguided allocation of resources: The assertion could lead to misguided allocation of resources where funds might be better spent on appropriate, high-quality office equipment that meets the actual needs of the employees and the business.

